esigns/issue-XXX/` and related docs. They must NOT directly write to `packages/`
or `apps/`.\n\n2. The widgetbook main.dart uses `Widgetbook.material`, `Widgetbo
okFolder`, `WidgetbookComponent`, `WidgetbookUseCase` - I should check if these 
