ue-XXX/` 下的设计资产" and "**禁止**在 Design-Only PR 中直接写入 `packages/`、`a
pps/` 或仓库根目录下的任何正式代码文件。" Deleting files from `packages/` is a v
iolation.\n\n**Major Issues:**\n3. **`SwipeCardStack` uses hardcoded `height: 50
