re if this is major or minor.\n\n5. **Golden test file paths are relative** - Th
e golden tests use `matchesGoldenFile(\'sw_action_button_variants.png\')` which 
is a relative path. In Flutter golden tests, relative paths are resolved from th
e test file\'s directory, which is correct here.\n\n6. **Widgetbook uses `Widget
book.material` etc.** - This matches the existing design-system widgetbook API (
