ver `HomePageSuccess`** - The `MatchSuccessDialog` returns a `Container(color: T
okens.modalOverlayColor, child: SafeArea(child: Center(child: ...)))`. When used
inside a `Stack` with `Positioned.fill`, the `Container` will fill the stack wit
h the overlay color. This works. However, the `SafeArea` inside the dialog might
behave differently when nested inside another `SafeArea` from `HomePageSuccess` 
which uses `SafeArea` on the Scaffold body. This is a minor layout concern.\n\nA
ctually, let me re-examine `MatchSuccessDialog` more carefully. It returns:\n```
