ild: Center(\n      child: AnimatedContainer(...)\n    )\n  )\n)\n```\n\nAnd `Ho
mePageMatchCreated` does:\n```dart\nStack(\n  children: [\n    const HomePageSuc
cess(),\n    Positioned.fill(\n      child: MatchSuccessDialog(...),\n    ),\n  
