e design-spec doesn\'t mention badge font tokens. Minor issue.\n\n20. **Golden t
est for `sw_action_button_test.dart` doesn\'t set surface size** - The SwipeCard
tests set `setSurfaceSize(const Size(375, 812))` but the SwActionButton test doe
sn\'t. This could lead to golden image size inconsistency across different envir
onments. Major? Maybe Minor since the scaffold is what gets captured and it shou
ld be stable enough.\n\n21. **Missing `kDebugMode` or other considerations** - N
ot applicable.\n\n22. **`preview.dart` doesn\'t use `intl`** - preview is a stan
dalone file, so acceptable.\n\nLet me compile the final assessment.\n\n**Summary
of issues:**\n\nBlocking:\n1. Design-Only PR modifies `packages/design-system/te
st/failures/` — violates the constraint that Design-Only PRs must ONLY touch `de
