age:social_world_design_system/social_world_design_system.dart` but are placed o
utside any Flutter package (no `pubspec.yaml` in `designs/issue-43/`), meaning t
hey cannot be compiled or run. The test code is non-functional.\n2. `MatchSucces
sDialog` uses `AnimatedContainer` with `curve: Curves.easeOutBack` but lacks an 
initial `transform` animation setup. The dialog will animate its container prope
rties but not the scale entry effect described in the design spec ("内容 scale(0
.9→1.0)"). The `AnimatedContainer` animates when its properties change, but sinc
e it\'s a StatelessWidget with no state changes, there is no entry animation at 
